{"tid":1936594,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"南韓總統等副部級以上官員未來4個月減薪3成","createTime":"2020-03-21T10:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T10:36:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ce2648a242649fff1339a5b06d1067ab5ccb8793","tid":1936594,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:14:45.000Z","msg":"南韓新增147人確診新型冠狀病毒，累計增至8799宗，大邱市和慶尚北道佔共109宗。<br />\n<br />\n南韓國務總理丁世均，緊急召開國務委員研討會，決定政府的副部長級以上高級公務員，包括總統文在寅及他本人，將在未來4個月減薪3成，企劃財政部會將款項用於支援因疫情遭受困難的國民。<br />\n<br />\n丁世均強烈建議集體感染風險較高的宗教、室內體育、娛樂等室內公共設施暫停運營半月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515976-20200321.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515976-20200321.htm&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F5NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=88d49b0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515976-20200321.htm&h=39af469a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515976-20200321.htm</a>"},{"pid":"79073e549b3599a7701dd9c8dd2679e5ac7734d7","tid":1936594,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:20:43.000Z","msg":"香港?<br />\n香港警察????"},{"pid":"8f3cb6014609e30d8fcfa308d2d7d2b250bcfec6","tid":1936594,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T10:36:21.000Z","msg":"明減三成，暗貪三倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}